Certainly! Here are a few examples of business plans for mobile apps that you can view online:

1. Uber Business Plan: <https://www.slideshare.net/RoshniKhatri1/business-plan-uber-55057935>
2. Tinder Business Plan: <https://www.slideshare.net/GoldenLimit/tinder-business-model>
3. Airbnb Business Plan: <https://www.slideshare.net/Teknowledge/airbnb-business-model-canvas-analysis>
4. Dropbox Business Plan: <https://www.slideshare.net/sharma0126/dropbox-business-model>

These examples can give you an idea of how to structure and present your own business plan for your app.
